                  "revisionId": 2775765,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "While Tek Enhance doesn't affect the cooldown time of abilities, only increases the buff duration, it results in proportionally higher uptime."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Tek Enhance",
                  "pageId": 1362673,
                  "revisionId": 2775765,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example, without this mod, Cat's Eye will have an effective uptime of 10 ÷ (10 + 20) = 33.33% . With this mod, the effective uptime will be (10 × (1+30%)) ÷ (10 × (1+30%) + 20) = 39.39% ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Tek Enhance",
                  "pageId": 1362673,
                  "revisionId": 2775765,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This mod only affects Kavat and Vulpaphyla abilities like Charm and Survival Instinct ."
                }
              },
